  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate whether methylphenidate (Ritalin) can actively
      induce emergence from general anesthesia in patients having a pancreaticoduodenectomy
      (Whipple procedure).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
